{"pageProps":{"post":{"id":"linux-vi","file":"linux-vi.md","excerptHtml":"<p class=\"mb-4\"><img src=\"https://tse1-mm.cn.bing.net/th/id/OIP-C.S7PWetAEkXIKI3Fgncz96wHaFF?pid=ImgDet&#x26;rs=1\" alt=\"vim\" class=\"mx-auto max-h-80\"></p>\n<h2 class=\"mb-4 text-xl font-bold pb-4 border-b border-slate-400/30\">vi特性</h2>\n<ul class=\"mb-4 list-disc\">\n<li class=\"ml-8\">vi编辑器包含两种模式，命令模式和输入模式</li>\n<li class=\"ml-8\">刚进入vi编辑器时是出于命令模式下</li>\n<li class=\"ml-8\">命令模式下的按键是对文件的命令</li>\n<li class=\"ml-8\">按<code class=\"px-1 py-0.5 mx-1 bg-slate-200 text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-700 rounded-md text-sm font-mono\">i</code>进入输入模式</li>\n<li class=\"ml-8\">按<code class=\"px-1 py-0.5 mx-1 bg-slate-200 text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-700 rounded-md text-sm font-mono\">Esc</code>退回到命令模式</li>\n</ul>\n","contentHtml":"<p class=\"mb-4\"><img src=\"https://tse1-mm.cn.bing.net/th/id/OIP-C.S7PWetAEkXIKI3Fgncz96wHaFF?pid=ImgDet&#x26;rs=1\" alt=\"vim\" class=\"mx-auto max-h-80\"></p>\n<h2 class=\"mb-4 text-xl font-bold pb-4 border-b border-slate-400/30\">vi特性</h2>\n<ul class=\"mb-4 list-disc\">\n<li class=\"ml-8\">vi编辑器包含两种模式，命令模式和输入模式</li>\n<li class=\"ml-8\">刚进入vi编辑器时是出于命令模式下</li>\n<li class=\"ml-8\">命令模式下的按键是对文件的命令</li>\n<li class=\"ml-8\">按<code class=\"px-1 py-0.5 mx-1 bg-slate-200 text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-700 rounded-md text-sm font-mono\">i</code>进入输入模式</li>\n<li class=\"ml-8\">按<code class=\"px-1 py-0.5 mx-1 bg-slate-200 text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-700 rounded-md text-sm font-mono\">Esc</code>退回到命令模式</li>\n</ul>\n<!--more-->\n<h2 class=\"mb-4 text-xl font-bold pb-4 border-b border-slate-400/30\">常用命令</h2>\n<table class=\"mb-4\">\n<thead class=\"bg-sky-200 dark:bg-sky-900\">\n<tr>\n<th class=\"px-2 border border-slate-400/30\">命令</th>\n<th class=\"px-2 border border-slate-400/30\">作用</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr class=\"odd:bg-slate-200 odd:dark:bg-slate-800 even:bg-slate-300 even:dark:bg-slate-700\">\n<td class=\"px-2 border border-slate-400/30\"><code class=\"px-1 py-0.5 mx-1 bg-slate-200 text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-700 rounded-md text-sm font-mono\">q</code></td>\n<td class=\"px-2 border border-slate-400/30\">退出vi</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"odd:bg-slate-200 odd:dark:bg-slate-800 even:bg-slate-300 even:dark:bg-slate-700\">\n<td class=\"px-2 border border-slate-400/30\"><code class=\"px-1 py-0.5 mx-1 bg-slate-200 text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-700 rounded-md text-sm font-mono\">wq</code></td>\n<td class=\"px-2 border border-slate-400/30\">保存并退出</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"odd:bg-slate-200 odd:dark:bg-slate-800 even:bg-slate-300 even:dark:bg-slate-700\">\n<td class=\"px-2 border border-slate-400/30\"><code class=\"px-1 py-0.5 mx-1 bg-slate-200 text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-700 rounded-md text-sm font-mono\">q!</code></td>\n<td class=\"px-2 border border-slate-400/30\">强制退出（不保存）</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"odd:bg-slate-200 odd:dark:bg-slate-800 even:bg-slate-300 even:dark:bg-slate-700\">\n<td class=\"px-2 border border-slate-400/30\"><code class=\"px-1 py-0.5 mx-1 bg-slate-200 text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-700 rounded-md text-sm font-mono\">j</code></td>\n<td class=\"px-2 border border-slate-400/30\">光标向下</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"odd:bg-slate-200 odd:dark:bg-slate-800 even:bg-slate-300 even:dark:bg-slate-700\">\n<td class=\"px-2 border border-slate-400/30\"><code class=\"px-1 py-0.5 mx-1 bg-slate-200 text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-700 rounded-md text-sm font-mono\">k</code></td>\n<td class=\"px-2 border border-slate-400/30\">光标向上</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"odd:bg-slate-200 odd:dark:bg-slate-800 even:bg-slate-300 even:dark:bg-slate-700\">\n<td class=\"px-2 border border-slate-400/30\"><code class=\"px-1 py-0.5 mx-1 bg-slate-200 text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-700 rounded-md text-sm font-mono\">h</code></td>\n<td class=\"px-2 border border-slate-400/30\">光标向左</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"odd:bg-slate-200 odd:dark:bg-slate-800 even:bg-slate-300 even:dark:bg-slate-700\">\n<td class=\"px-2 border border-slate-400/30\"><code class=\"px-1 py-0.5 mx-1 bg-slate-200 text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-700 rounded-md text-sm font-mono\">l</code></td>\n<td class=\"px-2 border border-slate-400/30\">光标向右</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"odd:bg-slate-200 odd:dark:bg-slate-800 even:bg-slate-300 even:dark:bg-slate-700\">\n<td class=\"px-2 border border-slate-400/30\"><code class=\"px-1 py-0.5 mx-1 bg-slate-200 text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-700 rounded-md text-sm font-mono\">0</code></td>\n<td class=\"px-2 border border-slate-400/30\">移动光标到行首</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"odd:bg-slate-200 odd:dark:bg-slate-800 even:bg-slate-300 even:dark:bg-slate-700\">\n<td class=\"px-2 border border-slate-400/30\"><code class=\"px-1 py-0.5 mx-1 bg-slate-200 text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-700 rounded-md text-sm font-mono\">$</code></td>\n<td class=\"px-2 border border-slate-400/30\">移动光标到行末</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"odd:bg-slate-200 odd:dark:bg-slate-800 even:bg-slate-300 even:dark:bg-slate-700\">\n<td class=\"px-2 border border-slate-400/30\"><code class=\"px-1 py-0.5 mx-1 bg-slate-200 text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-700 rounded-md text-sm font-mono\">u</code></td>\n<td class=\"px-2 border border-slate-400/30\">撤销</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"odd:bg-slate-200 odd:dark:bg-slate-800 even:bg-slate-300 even:dark:bg-slate-700\">\n<td class=\"px-2 border border-slate-400/30\"><code class=\"px-1 py-0.5 mx-1 bg-slate-200 text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-700 rounded-md text-sm font-mono\">x</code></td>\n<td class=\"px-2 border border-slate-400/30\">删除单个字符</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"odd:bg-slate-200 odd:dark:bg-slate-800 even:bg-slate-300 even:dark:bg-slate-700\">\n<td class=\"px-2 border border-slate-400/30\"><code class=\"px-1 py-0.5 mx-1 bg-slate-200 text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-700 rounded-md text-sm font-mono\">dd</code></td>\n<td class=\"px-2 border border-slate-400/30\">删除整行</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"odd:bg-slate-200 odd:dark:bg-slate-800 even:bg-slate-300 even:dark:bg-slate-700\">\n<td class=\"px-2 border border-slate-400/30\"><code class=\"px-1 py-0.5 mx-1 bg-slate-200 text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-700 rounded-md text-sm font-mono\">yy</code></td>\n<td class=\"px-2 border border-slate-400/30\">复制整行</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"odd:bg-slate-200 odd:dark:bg-slate-800 even:bg-slate-300 even:dark:bg-slate-700\">\n<td class=\"px-2 border border-slate-400/30\"><code class=\"px-1 py-0.5 mx-1 bg-slate-200 text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-700 rounded-md text-sm font-mono\">p</code></td>\n<td class=\"px-2 border border-slate-400/30\">粘贴</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n","content":"\n![vim](https://tse1-mm.cn.bing.net/th/id/OIP-C.S7PWetAEkXIKI3Fgncz96wHaFF?pid=ImgDet&rs=1)\n\n## vi特性\n- vi编辑器包含两种模式，命令模式和输入模式\n- 刚进入vi编辑器时是出于命令模式下\n- 命令模式下的按键是对文件的命令\n- 按`i`进入输入模式\n- 按`Esc`退回到命令模式\n\n<!--more-->\n\n## 常用命令\n\n| 命令 | 作用 |\n| ------------ | ------------ |\n| `q` |  退出vi |\n| `wq` | 保存并退出  |\n| `q!` |  强制退出（不保存） |\n| `j` | 光标向下 |\n| `k` |  光标向上 |\n| `h` | 光标向左 |\n| `l` |  光标向右 |\n| `0` | 移动光标到行首 |\n| `$` | 移动光标到行末 |\n| `u` | 撤销 |\n| `x` | 删除单个字符 |\n| `dd` | 删除整行 |\n| `yy` | 复制整行 |\n| `p` | 粘贴 |","data":{"title":"可能是史上最简单的vi/vim教程","date":"2017-06-21","tags":["Linux","vi"],"category":"Linux"},"isEmpty":false,"excerpt":"\n![vim](https://tse1-mm.cn.bing.net/th/id/OIP-C.S7PWetAEkXIKI3Fgncz96wHaFF?pid=ImgDet&rs=1)\n\n## vi特性\n- vi编辑器包含两种模式，命令模式和输入模式\n- 刚进入vi编辑器时是出于命令模式下\n- 命令模式下的按键是对文件的命令\n- 按`i`进入输入模式\n- 按`Esc`退回到命令模式\n\n"}},"__N_SSG":true}